Title: An Indian discovers the Portugal
DateModified: '2019-03-01'
DatePublished: '2019-03-01'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2019/applications/an-indian-discovers-the-portugal
SetInCountry: India
Category: Making a local connection
AuthorName: Sanmathi Kumar BS
AuthorCountry: India
Text: During the colonial period, Portuguese landed in the Indian subcontinent and
  introduced the culture, food and heritage. I wonder if they took any of our Indian
  culture, food and heritage back with them to their homeland. With this opportunity
  I would, as in an Indian, discovers would love to discover Portugal and try to find
  out we Indians imparted anything on their culture, food and heritage.
